[There is no specific treatment, including antivirals, currently available for AFM, and the putative etiological causes are quite varied. Patients who are hospitalized with severe respiratory illness may need to receive intensive supportive therapy. The long-term sequelae of AFM can be quite debilitating for a large percentage of infected children, with physiotherapy and physical rehabilitation required to improve mobility. - Mod.UBA

